tools.description:
Defines what content to display on the frontend for ShelterPoint claim status. Supported card types:
- claim_list -> data: {claims: [{claim_id, claim_type}]}
- claim_status -> data: {claim_id, claim_type, status, last_updated, action_required, action_details}
- benefit_info -> data: {claim_id, claim_type, weekly_benefit, coverage, max_duration, payment}
- escalation -> data: {}
All data must be passed as a JSON string. Empty fields are acceptable.
